## Roles & Responsibilities

### Incident Lead (IL)

- Directs triage and technical actions
- Ensures timelines, decisions and evidence are captured

### Comms Lead (CL)

- Manages internal and external communications
- Maintains communication cadence based on incident priority
- Owns PagerDuty Status Page updates

### Subject Matter Responders (SMRs)

- Investigate and remediate issues
- Document commands, configuration changes and findings

### Escalation Contacts

- PM and DM (for P1/P2 incidents and major customer impact)
- Cyber Security for suspected security or data incidents

