## Communications Plan

| Priority | Initial Response | Ongoing Updates |
|-----------|-----------------|-----------------|
| **P1** | Within 20 minutes | Hourly + end-of-day summary |
| **P2** | Within 60 minutes | Every 2 hours + end-of-day summary |
| **P3** | Within 2 hours | One update after 2 business days if ongoing |
| **P4** | Within 1 business day | One update after 5 business days if ongoing |

### Channels

**Internal**

- Slack (`#analytical-platform`)

**External**

- PagerDuty Status Page
- Email / Teams (if required)

### Escalations

- Notify PM/DM for P1 and P2 incidents
- Involve Cyber Security for suspected security or data incidents
- Engage vendors where appropriate

